    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of the species Celtis laevigata. It is used for furniture, cooperage, vehicle bodies, and wood ware.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
